Jules (Daniel Arends) en Max (Tim Haars) made a pact never

live a party-life in which they sleep with a different
girl every day. However this changes when Jules starts to
date Anna (Sylvia Hoeks) and Max falls in love with her.
Can their bromance overcome this love triangle. Although
the makers of this movie claim this movie is a romcom,
